<h1>Your ride request is active</h1>

<p>Hi,</p>

<p>Thanks for using HopHub!</p>

<p>Your ride request for the event "<strong><%= @ride_request.event.name %></strong>" has been confirmed. We will email you when a matching offer is posted.</p>

<p><a href="<%= event_url(@ride_request.event) %>" class="button">View event page</a></p>

<p>If you no longer want to receive notifications for this request, you can delete it with this secret link. Please keep it to yourself:</p>

<% destroy_url = event_ride_request_destroy_url(@ride_request.event, @ride_request, token: @ride_request.token, locale: I18n.locale) %>
<div class="secret-link"><a href="<%= destroy_url %>"><%= destroy_url %></a></div>

<p>Your request will be automatically removed when the event ends.</p>

<p class="signoff">Kind regards from the HopHub platform.</p>
